Skills.Name: One, Two, Three!
Skills.Description: Inflicts 3-hit DMG (<color=red>{0}%</color> + <color=red>{1}%</color> + <color=red>{2}%</color>) on all enemies. Further lowers CRIT DEF based on total <code=900,param=900><color=#3398f1>Mystic Power</color> (Stacked) on all characters in battle multiplied by {4}% for 10s (Max. {5}%).
Skills.ShortDescription: Inflicts 3-hit DMG on all enemies, lowers CRIT DEF based on total Mystic Power in battle

Skills.Name: Training Triumph!
Skills.Description: Inflicts <code=400,param=256><color=#3398f1>Weakness</color> ({0}% of skill user's ATK) on single enemy with highest ATK for 8s. Also inflicts 3-hit DMG (<color=red>{1}%</color> + <color=red>{2}%</color> + <color=red>{3}%</color>). Also inflicts 2x <code=900,param=900><color=#3398f1>Mystic Power</color> for 25s. Further lowers DEF by <color=red>{6}%</color> for 10s if Red Elemental.
Skills.ShortDescription: Inflicts Weakness, 3-hit DMG and Mystic Power on single enemy, lowers DEF if Red Elemental

Skills.Name: Secret Onstage
Skills.Description: Cancels all Buff effects on single enemy. Also inflicts 3-hit DMG (<color=red>{1}%</color> + <color=red>{2}%</color> + <color=red>{3}%</color>). Also inflicts DMG based on total <code=900,param=900><color=#3398f1>Mystic Power</color> (Stacked) on all characters in battle multiplied by {5}% (Max. {6}%). Further inflicts <code=400,param=205><color=#3398f1>Seal</color> for 5s.
Skills.ShortDescription: Cancels all Buff effects, inflicts 3-hit DMG on single enemy. Further inflicts DMG based on total Mystic Power in battle, and Seal

Skills.Name: Strike Combo
Skills.Description: Inflicts <color=red>75.00%-1500.00%</color> DMG according to Combo Bonus.

Skills.Name: Troubled School Girl
Skills.Description: At start of Wave, lowers DMG Inflicted for all enemies by <color=red>{1}%</color> multiplied by number of Uniforms in party for 60s. Further lowers Speed by <color=red>{4}%</color> multiplied by number of Uniforms in party for 60s.
Skills.ShortDescription: At start of Wave, lowers DMG Inflicted and Speed of all enemies based on number of Uniforms in party
